<article id="post-301" class="post-301 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-banken tag-fidor tag-konten">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/07/24/fidor-bank-neue-agbs/" rel="bookmark">Fidor Bank &#8211; neue AGBs</a></h1>

				<div class="entry-meta">
			Veröffentlicht am <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/07/24/fidor-bank-neue-agbs/" title="13:52" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-07-24T13:52:11+00:00" pubdate>24. Juli 2013</time></a><span class="byline"> von <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/author/ambajorat/" title="Zeige alle Beiträge von André M. Bajorat" rel="author">André M. Bajorat</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p><strong>Nutzer der Fidor Bank aufgepasst:</strong></p>
<p>Ihr müsst auf der Webseite der Fidor Bank die neuen ABGs akzeptieren. Erst dann kann figo eure Fidor-Konten wieder im Blick behalten.</p>
<p><a href="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20.png"><img data-attachment-id="302" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/07/24/fidor-bank-neue-agbs/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20.png" data-orig-size="1580,1230" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="Bildschirmfoto 2013-07-24 um 15.48.20" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20.png?w=558" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-302" alt="Bildschirmfoto 2013-07-24 um 15.48.20" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20.png?w=300&#038;h=233" width="300" height="233" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20.png?w=300 300w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20.png?w=600 600w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bildschirmfoto-2013-07-24-um-15-48-20.png?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
