<article id="post-276" class="post-276 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-banken category-paypal tag-paypal tag-paypal-account">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/05/08/paypal-kontoeinrichtung-angepasst/" rel="bookmark">PayPal Kontoeinrichtung angepasst</a></h1>

				<div class="entry-meta">
			Veröffentlicht am <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/05/08/paypal-kontoeinrichtung-angepasst/" title="08:12" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-05-08T08:12:29+00:00" pubdate>8. Mai 2013</time></a><span class="byline"> von <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/author/ambajorat/" title="Zeige alle Beiträge von André M. Bajorat" rel="author">André M. Bajorat</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p><strong>Das Einrichten eines PayPal Accounts in figo war ja auch bisher schon möglich &#8211; allerdings brauchtet Ihr dafür <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/23/einrichten-des-paypal-accounts/">erweitere Daten</a> von PayPal und musstet diese manuell in figo eingeben. Um es euch leichter zu machen haben wir diesen Prozess deutlich vereinfacht und Ihr könnt euer PayPal-Konto jetzt mit Eingabe eurer Standard-PayPal Benutzerdaten (eMail und Password) in figo einrichten.</strong></p>
<p>Leider müsst Ihr aber weiter eine Voraussetzung erfüllen: Ihr braucht eine API-Berechtigung von PayPal. Wenn Ihr diese noch nicht habt, hier der Weg dorthin:</p>
<ul>
<li>Loggt euch mit euren Benutzerdaten bei PayPal direkt ein.</li>
<li>Wechselt auf den Menüpunkt “Mein Profil”.</li>
</ul>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_278" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt1.png"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-278" data-attachment-id="278" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/05/08/paypal-kontoeinrichtung-angepasst/schritt1/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt1.png" data-orig-size="2042,1316" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="schritt1" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt1.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt1.png?w=558" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-278 " alt="schritt1" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt1.png?w=300&#038;h=193" width="300" height="193" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt1.png?w=300 300w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt1.png?w=600 600w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt1.png?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-278" class="wp-caption-text">Unter dem Punkt &#8222;mehr&#8220;</p></div>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_282" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt2.png"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-282" data-attachment-id="282" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/05/08/paypal-kontoeinrichtung-angepasst/schritt2/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt2.png" data-orig-size="2106,1284" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="schritt2" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt2.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt2.png?w=558" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-282" alt="schritt2" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt2.png?w=300&#038;h=182" width="300" height="182" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt2.png?w=300 300w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt2.png?w=597 597w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt2.png?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-282" class="wp-caption-text">dort unter &#8222;Verkäufer/Händler&#8220; den &#8222;API-Zugriff&#8220; aktualisieren</p></div>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_281" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt3.png"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-281" data-attachment-id="281" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/05/08/paypal-kontoeinrichtung-angepasst/schritt3/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt3.png" data-orig-size="1594,1332" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="schritt3" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt3.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt3.png?w=558" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-281" alt="schritt3" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt3.png?w=300&#038;h=250" width="300" height="250" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt3.png?w=300 300w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt3.png?w=598 598w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt3.png?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-281" class="wp-caption-text">hier die &#8222;API-Berechtigung&#8220; anfordern</p></div>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_280" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt4.png"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-280" data-attachment-id="280" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/05/08/paypal-kontoeinrichtung-angepasst/schritt4/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt4.png" data-orig-size="1598,1350" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="schritt4" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt4.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt4.png?w=558" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-280" alt="schritt4" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt4.png?w=300&#038;h=253" width="300" height="253" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt4.png?w=300 300w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt4.png?w=600 600w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt4.png?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-280" class="wp-caption-text">und diese API-Signatur anfordern</p></div>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_279" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt5.png"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-279" data-attachment-id="279" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/05/08/paypal-kontoeinrichtung-angepasst/schritt5/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt5.png" data-orig-size="1606,1352" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="schritt5" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt5.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt5.png?w=558" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-279" alt="schritt5" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt5.png?w=300&#038;h=252" width="300" height="252" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt5.png?w=300 300w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt5.png?w=600 600w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/schritt5.png?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-279" class="wp-caption-text">Mit drücken von Fertig ist alles geschehen</p></div>
<ul>
<li>Damit hast Du die PayPal API-Berechtigung angefordert.</li>
<li>Die nun erstellten API-Zugangsdaten werden automatisch bei Erstellung/Synchronisation des Kontos von figo abgerufen</li>
</ul>
<p>Jetzt kannst Du deinen PayPal Account unter Eingabe deiner eMail Adresse und des Passwords einrichten!</p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
	<footer class="entry-meta">
								<span class="cat-links">
				Veröffentlicht in <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/category/banken/" rel="category tag">Banken</a>, <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/category/paypal/" rel="category tag">PayPal</a>			</span>
			
			<span class="tag-links">Verschlagwortet mit <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/tag/paypal/" rel="tag">PayPal</a>, <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/tag/paypal-account/" rel="tag">paypal account</a></span>		
				<span class="comments-link"><a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/05/08/paypal-kontoeinrichtung-angepasst/#respond">Hinterlasse einen Kommentar</a></span>
		
			</footer><!-- .entry-meta -->
