		<div class="entry-content">
		<p><strong>Eine neue Bank ist dabei: <a href="http://www.bankofscotland.de/bos/de.html">Die Bank of Scotland</a>.</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/foto.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="210" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2013/03/13/bank-of-scotland-jetzt-dabei/foto-5/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/foto.jpg" data-orig-size="640,1136" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="Foto" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/foto.jpg?w=169" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/foto.jpg?w=558" loading="lazy" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-210" alt="Foto" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/foto.jpg?w=169&#038;h=300" width="169" height="300" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/foto.jpg?w=169 169w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/foto.jpg?w=338 338w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/foto.jpg?w=85 85w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /></a></p>
