<article id="post-119" class="post-119 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-funktionen category-sicherheit tag-code tag-entsperren tag-sicherheit tag-swipe">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/25/app-sperre-und-sperrcode-in-figo/" rel="bookmark">App-Sperre und Sperrcode in figo</a></h1>

				<div class="entry-meta">
			Veröffentlicht am <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/25/app-sperre-und-sperrcode-in-figo/" title="12:14" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-12-25T12:14:53+00:00" pubdate>25. Dezember 2012</time></a><span class="byline"> von <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/author/ambajorat/" title="Zeige alle Beiträge von André M. Bajorat" rel="author">André M. Bajorat</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Standardmässig schliesst sich figo wenn Du die App verlässt.<br />
Hin und wieder kann es aber sinnvoll sein die App erst nach einem bestimmten Zeitraum sperren zu lassen um zum Beispiel <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/23/einrichten-des-paypal-accounts/">Daten für die Kontoeinrichtung</a> zu übernehmen. Dies kann im Hauptmenü individuell eingestellt werden.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_121" style="width: 179px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/25/app-sperre-und-sperrcode-in-figo/img_4745/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-121"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-121" data-attachment-id="121" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/25/app-sperre-und-sperrcode-in-figo/img_4745/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4745.png" data-orig-size="640,1136" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="IMG_4745" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4745.png?w=169" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4745.png?w=558" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-121 " alt="IMG_4745" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4745.png?w=169&#038;h=300" width="169" height="300" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4745.png?w=169 169w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4745.png?w=338 338w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4745.png?w=85 85w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-121" class="wp-caption-text">Einstellungen für die App-Sperre</p></div>
<p>Dort kann zum Beispiel auch ein neuer Entsperr-Code eingeben werden.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_123" style="width: 179px" class="wp-caption alignleft"><a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/25/app-sperre-und-sperrcode-in-figo/img_4746/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-123"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-123" data-attachment-id="123" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/25/app-sperre-und-sperrcode-in-figo/img_4746/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4746.png" data-orig-size="640,1136" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="IMG_4746" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4746.png?w=169" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4746.png?w=558" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-123" alt="IMG_4746" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4746.png?w=169&#038;h=300" width="169" height="300" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4746.png?w=169 169w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4746.png?w=338 338w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4746.png?w=85 85w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-123" class="wp-caption-text">Eingabe des Entsperr-Codes</p></div>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
	<footer class="entry-meta">
