<article id="post-80" class="post-80 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-funktionen category-sicherheit tag-loschen tag-sicherheit">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/23/wie-kann-ich-meinen-figo-account-loschen/" rel="bookmark">Wie kann ich meinen figo-Account löschen?</a></h1>

				<div class="entry-meta">
			Veröffentlicht am <a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/23/wie-kann-ich-meinen-figo-account-loschen/" title="17:43" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-12-23T17:43:00+00:00" pubdate>23. Dezember 2012</time></a><span class="byline"> von <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/author/ambajorat/" title="Zeige alle Beiträge von André M. Bajorat" rel="author">André M. Bajorat</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Direkt in der App. Mit dem Löschen Deines Accounts werden auch alle deine Daten bei uns gelöscht.</p>
<p><a href="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/23/wie-kann-ich-meinen-figo-account-loschen/img_4732/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-81"><img data-attachment-id="81" data-permalink="https://figoapp.wordpress.com/2012/12/23/wie-kann-ich-meinen-figo-account-loschen/img_4732/#main" data-orig-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4732.png" data-orig-size="640,1136" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="IMG_4732" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4732.png?w=169" data-large-file="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4732.png?w=558" loading="lazy" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-81" alt="IMG_4732" src="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4732.png?w=169&#038;h=300" width="169" height="300" srcset="https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4732.png?w=169 169w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4732.png?w=338 338w, https://figoapp.files.wordpress.com/2012/12/img_4732.png?w=85 85w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
	<footer class="entry-meta">
